  "keyFeatures": [
    "Standalone-first Angular architecture (v17-21 compatible)",
    "50+ premium UI components with glassmorphism design",
    "Native CSS theming with dark mode support",
    "Built-in accessibility (a11y) with ARIA support",
    "OnPush change detection for optimal performance",
    "Drag-and-drop functionality with Atlassian Pragmatic DnD",
    "Mobile-ready responsive components",
    "TypeScript-first with full type safety"
